                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-24-defend252 t18190915-24-punish135"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 40.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Richardson.</p>
